      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$19,500 - Check out this dependable ride that's perfect for anyone looking for a solid value! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, it remains a reliable performer that gets the job done. This is a great opportunity to own a functional vehicle at a price that won't break the bank!",
