    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable mode of transportation without the price tag of a newer model. The exterior does show some signs of age, including a few noticeable scratches on the passenger side and minor dings from parking lots. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some fading and typical wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car is sound and starts up reliably, though it may require some routine maintenance like new brake pads in the near future. It\u2019s a functional, honest car that gets the job done.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no chips or scratches, while the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear on the leather or trim. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine runs silently and all systems function exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved example that has been maintained to the highest possible standard.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
